  <div>
    <div class="article">
      <p>My name is Sebastian Witowski and I'm an independent Python consultant, freelancer, and international speaker based in Poland.</p>
      <div class="md:w-1/2 w-full mx-auto">
        {%- image '_assets/images/me-talking-ep2022.jpg', 'Me speaking at EuroPython 2022 conference', '', 'rounded-3xl' -%}
