  <div class="article">
    <p>When I don't work, I play video games. I'm a huge fan of From Software games, with my favorite one being "Dark Souls 2". It was my gateway drug to the genre, so suck it up haters.</p>
    <p>During the winter, I go snowboarding. During the summer, I do enduro biking and (recently) surfing. And all year round, I do powerlifting. On the 15th of December 2017, I joined the 1000-pound club. </p>
